item.title: MOSD episode3 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode3 by TheZakW

The mystery continues when Roderick goes missing! Can Nancy and Nigel find him before it's too late! What if they don't? Will Nancy remarry? Does she already have her eye on the cute bag boy at the grocery store? Will Roderick haunt her when they go out on dates?

item.title: MOSD episode1 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode1 by TheZakW

The first episode in the startling new mystery serial. Roderick and Nancy are having dinner at Nigel's house. I'm sure nothing will go wrong. No, nothing at all. Should be a pleasant evening, with no murders whatsoever. Yes I'm quite sure of it.

item.title: MOSD episode2 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode2 by TheZakW

The next exciting chapter. Will Roderick, Nancy, and Nigel get out alive? Can they solve the mystery and find the murderer? Will Nancy ever get something to eat? Does anyone actually care? Find out the answers to some if not none of these questions.

item.title: MOSD episode6 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode6 by TheZakW

Roderick, Nancy, and Nigel find themselves fighting for their lives in a raging fire. Who started the fire? Was it Billy Joel? He keeps telling us it was always burning since the world's been turning but really why should we trust him?

item.title: MOSD episode4 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode4 by TheZakW

The search for Roderick continues. Also, deep dark secrets are revealed. What are they? You'll have to listen to find out. Or you could ask someone who already has listened to it, but good luck finding someone like that.

item.title: MOSD episode5 by TheZakW
item.description:
MOSD episode5 by TheZakW

A surly gangster brings some new information to light. Also, Nancy throws up and Roderick sits down. What?! Crazy! How could you live with yourself if you missed this exciting chapter? You probably couldn't. So for your own safety, please press play.
